Package org.flywaydb.core.api.callback

Class BaseFlywayCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.flywaydb.core.api.callback.BaseFlywayCallback
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FlywayCallback, ConfigurationAware
    Deprecated. 
    Implement Callback instead. Will be removed in Flyway 6.0.

    @Deprecated
public abstract class BaseFlywayCallback
extends Object
implements FlywayCallback, ConfigurationAware
    Convenience base no-op implementation of FlywayCallback. Extend this class if you want to implement just a few callback methods without having to provide no-op methods yourself.

    This implementation also provides direct access to the FlywayConfiguration as field.
